#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""delegate-to-antigravity — legacy keyed-switchboard dispatch. NOT the sanctioned
Antigravity lane. Under the no-API-key policy the keyed remote route this script
drives is non-functional for real Antigravity identity/review work — use it only
for diagnostics.

THE SANCTIONED ANTIGRAVITY LANE IS `aq-collab-round`: it drops a task file into
`.agent/collaboration/antigravity-inbox/<name>.md`; the Antigravity IDE picks it
up via its OWN Google OAuth session and writes the response back. No API key,
no switchboard, no headless keyed call. Use that for any real Antigravity review,
PRD, plan, or research task.

What this script actually does: routes through the local switchboard
(http://127.0.0.1:8085) using a remote profile that forces provider=remote
against Google Gemini direct (generativelanguage.googleapis.com/v1beta/openai).
Under the no-key policy there is no valid Google AI Studio key wired to that
profile, so the keyed call fails (commonly 502/503/400/401/403) and this script
falls back to the local Qwen3-35B profile (local-coding) — a local completion,
not an Antigravity review. `--loop` (aq-antigravity-agent) additionally refuses
to silently mask a remote failure as a hybrid-coordinator RAG result (see
.agents/plans/antigravity-lane-restoration/ROUTING-FIX-PROPOSAL.md, D1/D2) — a
failed keyed dispatch surfaces as an explicit failure, not fake output.

Do NOT add or rotate any secret to try to make this path work; it is
policy-forbidden, not merely broken. Route real Antigravity work through
`aq-collab-round` instead.

Note: @google/gemini-cli (npm) and the oauth-personal/Code Assist path are RETIRED
as of 2026-07 (IneligibleTierError for free-tier). Do NOT use 'gemini' npm binary.

Usage:
  delegate-to-antigravity --prompt "task description"   # background dispatch
  delegate-to-antigravity --prompt "..." --wait         # blocking, prints output
  delegate-to-antigravity --check <task-id>             # read output
  delegate-to-antigravity --status <task-id>            # check status
  delegate-to-antigravity --list                        # list all tasks
  delegate-to-antigravity --prompt "..." --loop         # agentic loop (tool use)
"""

